full_text: Screened by NARA, 8/15/2023 DUPLICATE Ene 3 RollNo. 81345 Serial No. 36588 BOARD OF HIGH SCHOOL & INTERMEDIATE EDUCATION UTTAR PRADESH ***Seal*** HIGH SCHOOL EXAMINATION 1951 Certified that Dharmendra Swarup passed the High School Examination in second division of March/April 1951, from Government Intermediate College, Allahabad, and he obtained distinction in nil.
